Dear Nadia,=20

=20

Apologies for the delayed reply and thank you for your six emails dating fr=
om 16 January 2026 to 30 January 2026 of which the content and the attached =
documents have been noted.=20

=20

Kindly note as of your email dated 16 January 2026 (attached) filing an app=
lication, please note you are to produce this application on the Court form =
N244 Application notice and provide the payment of =C2=A3313 for the court to co=
nsider.=20

=20

As of this I kindly ask for you to file the correct application with fee at=
 your earliest opportunity if you wish to proceed with your request.=20

=20

=20

If replying by email, please use the following address:=20

administrativecourtoffice.caseprogression@justice.gov.uk=20

=20

=20

Kind regards

=20

Asif Bhurani

